<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="FajnNederlands">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#C94A0A">
  <title>FajnNederlands 🇳🇱</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --orange: #C94A0A;
      --orange-light: #F26522;
      --orange-pale: #FEF0E7;
      --navy: #1A2744;
      --navy-mid: #2E3F6A;
      --cream: #FDF8F2;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --gray: #6B7280;
      --gray-light: #F3F4F6;
      --green: #16A34A;
      --red: #DC2626;
      --radius: 16px;
      --shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,39,68,0.10);
      --shadow-lg: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,39,68,0.16);
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--cream);
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      color: var(--navy);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #app {
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* SCREENS */
    .screen {
      display: none;
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }
    .screen.active { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

    /* HOME SCREEN */
    .home-header {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 48px 24px 32px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .home-header::before {
      content: '🇳🇱';
      font-size: 120px;
      position: absolute;
      right: -20px;
      top: -10px;
      opacity: 0.12;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .home-header h1 {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .home-header h1 span { color: var(--orange-light); }
    .home-header p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .progress-bar-wrap {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 99px;
      height: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .progress-bar-fill {
      background: var(--orange-light);
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 99px;
      transition: width 0.5s ease;
    }
    .progress-label {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .modules-grid {
      padding: 20px 16px 32px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .module-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    }
    .module-card:active { transform: scale(0.98); box-shadow: none; }
    .module-card.done { border-color: var(--green); }

    .module-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 26px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .module-info { flex: 1; }
    .module-info h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .module-info p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .module-arrow {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .module-card.done .module-arrow { color: var(--green); }

    /* MODULE SCREEN */
    .module-header {
      padding: 20px 20px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      background: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 #E5E7EB;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .back-btn {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--gray-light);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--navy);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    }
    .module-header-info h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
    }
    .module-header-info p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .situations-list {
      padding: 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .situation-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .situation-header {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    }
    .situation-ctx {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .situation-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .situation-toggle {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--gray);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .situation-card.open .situation-toggle { transform: rotate(180deg); }

    .situation-body {
      display: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
    }
    .situation-card.open .situation-body { display: block; }

    .phrase-row {
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    }
    .phrase-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .phrase-nl {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .phrase-cs {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .phrase-pron {
      display: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--orange);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 4px;
      background: var(--orange-pale);
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .quiz-btn-wrap {
      padding: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .quiz-btn {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--orange);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .quiz-btn:active { background: #A33D08; }

    /* QUIZ SCREEN */
    .quiz-header {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 20px 20px 24px;
    }
    .quiz-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .quiz-top h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .quiz-progress-text {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .quiz-bar-wrap {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 99px;
      height: 5px;
    }
    .quiz-bar-fill {
      background: var(--orange-light);
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 99px;
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    .quiz-body {
      padding: 24px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .quiz-question-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .quiz-question-text {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .quiz-subtext {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .quiz-options {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .quiz-option {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 2px solid #E5E7EB;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: inherit;
      color: var(--navy);
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: left;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .quiz-option:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
    .quiz-option.correct {
      background: #DCFCE7;
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: var(--green);
    }
    .quiz-option.wrong {
      background: #FEE2E2;
      border-color: var(--red);
      color: var(--red);
    }
    .quiz-option.disabled { cursor: default; }

    .quiz-feedback {
      display: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .quiz-feedback.correct-fb {
      background: #DCFCE7;
      color: var(--green);
    }
    .quiz-feedback.wrong-fb {
      background: #FEE2E2;
      color: var(--red);
    }
    .quiz-feedback.show { display: block; }
    .quiz-feedback .correct-ans {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 400;
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .next-btn {
      background: var(--orange);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      display: none;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .next-btn.show { display: block; }
    .next-btn:active { background: #A33D08; }

    /* RESULT SCREEN */
    .result-screen {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .result-emoji { font-size: 64px; }
    .result-score {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 52px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
    }
    .result-score span { color: var(--orange); }
    .result-msg {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--navy);
    }
    .result-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--gray);
      max-width: 280px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .result-btn {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 16px 32px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
    }

    /* PRONUNCIATION NOTE */
    .pron-note {
      background: var(--orange-pale);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--orange);
      margin: 0 16px 12px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .pron-note h4 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--orange);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .pron-note p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .speak-icon { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.5; }
    .phrase-row:active .speak-icon { opacity: 1; }
    .tap-hint {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--gray);
      padding: 0 0 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">
  <!-- HOME -->
  <div class="screen active" id="screen-home">
    <div class="home-header">
      <h1>Fajn<span>Nederlands</span></h1>
      <p>Holandština pro každý den 🇳🇱</p>
      <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
        <div class="progress-bar-fill" id="home-progress" style="width: 0%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-label" id="home-progress-label">0 z 5 modulů dokončeno</div>
    </div>
    <div class="modules-grid" id="modules-grid"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- MODULE -->
  <div class="screen" id="screen-module">
    <div class="module-header">
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="showHome()">←</button>
      <div class="module-header-info">
        <h2 id="module-title-header">Modul</h2>
        <p id="module-subtitle-header">Klikni na frázi pro výslovnost</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pron-note">
      <h4>🔊 Jak číst výslovnost</h4>
      <p><b>ch/ch</b> = jako v „Bach" · <b>ej</b> = jako v „hej" · <b>oe</b> = jako „ú" · <b>ü</b> = jako německé ü · <b>aa/ee</b> = dlouhé a/e</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tap-hint">Klikni na frázi → výslovnost</div>
    <div class="situations-list" id="situations-list"></div>
    <div class="quiz-btn-wrap">
      <button class="quiz-btn" onclick="startQuiz()">🎯 Procvičit slovíčka</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- QUIZ -->
  <div class="screen" id="screen-quiz">
    <div class="quiz-header">
      <div class="quiz-top">
        <button class="back-btn" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white" onclick="backToModule()">←</button>
        <h2 id="quiz-module-name">Kvíz</h2>
        <span class="quiz-progress-text" id="quiz-progress-text">1/10</span>
      </div>
      <div class="quiz-bar-wrap">
        <div class="quiz-bar-fill" id="quiz-bar" style="width:10%"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-body">
      <div>
        <div class="quiz-question-label">Jak se holandsky řekne:</div>
        <div class="quiz-question-text" id="quiz-question"></div>
        <div class="quiz-subtext" id="quiz-context"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="quiz-options" id="quiz-options"></div>
      <div class="quiz-feedback" id="quiz-feedback"></div>
      <button class="next-btn" id="next-btn" onclick="nextQuestion()">Další →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RESULT -->
  <div class="screen" id="screen-result">
    <div class="result-screen">
      <div class="result-emoji" id="result-emoji">🎉</div>
      <div class="result-score" id="result-score">8<span>/10</span></div>
      <div class="result-msg" id="result-msg">Výborně!</div>
      <div class="result-sub" id="result-sub">Pokračuj tak dál.</div>
      <button class="result-btn" onclick="backToModule()">Zpět na modul</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

